description: '''Bri Money''' (born March 9, 2007), professionally known as '''Jnhygs''' (stylized as '''jnhygs'''; pronounced '''''jin-higgs''''') is an American rapper and songwriter based in [[Alabama]], known for her songs "Xtayalive", "[[Shake That Shit!|Shake That Shit]]", and "[[Smoke It Off]]" with [[Lumi Athena]], which she is responsible for the vocals of, debuted at number 12 on the US [[Hot Dance/Electronic Songs]] chart.
